![Robot](images/robot.jpg)

## Setup Instructions

1. Install Arduino IDE
2. Install ESP32 board package
3. Connect PCA9685 to ESP32 via I2C
4. Upload the Arduino code
5. Connect to ESP32 IP address in browser
6. Control the robot wirelessly
